snippet.title: Chevelle - "Saferwaters" | Haider Ali (Guitar Cover) #Shorts
snippet.description:
“Saferwaters” by @CheVelle from the album Vena Sera — released in 2007 under Epic Records, and produced by Michael Baskette at Studio at the Palms in Paradise, NV, USA — guitar performance by @Haider Ali.

• Subscribe
https://www.youtube.com/haidertonight?sub_confirmation=1

• Thoughts
So, this is the beginning of something very exciting, folks. Starting tonight, I will be posting short guitar covers every single day of the week, and full-length guitar covers only on the weekends — this will allow me to turn out more content for you fine people, and I'll be able to be more creative, so sit back, relax, and enjoy this first song, and share your thoughts in the comments below, cheers!
